RouteOptions
public static enum RouteOptions.Type
extends java.lang.Enum<RouteOptions.Type>

Represents different types of routing, such as by speed or by distance.

Note: a Type has no effect on RouteOptions.TransportMode.PEDESTRIAN transport mode, since it always uses FASTEST (if SHORTEST is set as the Type when one of these TransportMode types is selected, it will be reset to FASTEST when a Route is calculated).
